N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 78.45 - Garbage or other refuse disposal restricted

State Regulations

No person shall place, discharge, or deposit in any manner
offal, garbage, or any refuse in or upon any part of the airport, except at
such places and under such conditions as the airport operator may, from time to
time, prescribe. Notes
